target_assessment.explanation: The finding about _withdrawActiveVotingPower is incorrect. The issue is not about gas exhaustion but about incorrect proposal tracking. The function does not iterate through all known proposal IDs when unlocking - it only checks the proposals the user has voted on. The root cause is the misuse of isProposalOpen() as an 'isProposalStillOpen()' function, which incorrectly removes proposals that haven't started yet from tracking.
